				<td colspan="2"><span>Hello all, I just had a question about a bard dealing with pacify and CC. I started a ldon group, I don't remember the exact make up it was like me a shaman, necro, beast, druid, and a bard, one other I believe.. but I can't remember what. A ghetto group I know, but it's tough to get anyone to do a SRO group, I was hoping between the bard could pacify, and if we got any adds the necro and bard could CC, and I would root any others left. First off the bard was very very upset that he had to pull, then everytime he pulled he got 3-5 adds, we had maybe 4 wipeouts, or close to wipeouts most everyone zoned. I always thought that bards could pacify mobs decently, or at least CC a bit. This guys seemed to do neither. Now I understand things go wrong, so I didn't say anything I figured I would ask here since you guys would be the experts. Does it sound like this guy is ebayed, or did he just have pretty bad luck?</span></td>
